attachments.fallback: David Keatts moved the card ads: Hey guys - since we're moving into November, we did a quick audit of the site and came up with a few viewability recommendations. We've seen a good bump on a few of our other sites by implementing these sort of changes (mostly increased CPM). But - like always - the changes are up to you.  remove lower down 728x90 (third down) and replace with a second sidebar ad below the top page content on the lefthand side float both sidebar ads so they scroll with user down page Doing this should set everything up pretty well - we have a few more tweaks after we get things rolling on the viewability side to bump it up even more. from EDHREC Let's Do Soon to Doing.
